      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-pressure dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. The chassis has been maintained with technical rigor, including a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed suspension bushings to preserve the factory-spec kinematics. While the paint and interior exhibit minor signs of use consistent with its history, the mechanical vitals are excellent, with recent rod bearing replacement and valve clearance adjustments performed. This is a mechanically sorted performance icon that prioritizes tactile feedback and engine harmonics.",
